Text: *yawn*
...I slept well.
What time is it? Ah, whatever...

Guess I'll get started on the research the Garden
asked me to do...

Eta used to be able to conduct her research as she
pleased, but as the Garden expanded, requests for
her expertise increased.
Hup...
Let's see. Work list...work list... There it is.

What's this...? "Modified slime" and a "device to cut
it"? What are they gonna use that for? A disguise?

Oh well...the deadline's close, so let's get it done
quickly...

Handling slime...is my forte... I'll just apply the
principle of solidifying magic...and...

But I'll need expensive materials for this...
Let's just call it a necessary expense.

Look at me worrying about expenses.
I'm all grown up...

I used to think Gamma was rolling in endless streams
of cash, but as I've matured, I've come to understand
that money is finite.
I'll just need to do this...and thisâ€”
A few hours later.

If I utilize this theory...I should be able to
increase energy efficiency...by 18%...
...Alright, done! It's perfect!

I managed to finish the device at top speed...
and meet my quota.
Alright...next request...
Hmm? What's this?

Modified gummies...that make you stronger just by
eating them?
Why does everyone like gummies so much?

I tried to balance nutritional value with flavor for
the original version, but...

I won't take responsibility for how it turns out...
this time around...

Ingredients that can enhance strength... The blood of
a monster? Of a wild boar? ...Oh, how about the blood
of the royals?

Besides...it doesn't necessarily have to be something
edible. Yeah. Might be worth adding some finely
grounded mithril. I should try every possibility out
there...

Oh, but I haven't considered the flavor or how
difficult they'll be to get ahold of...

Oh well. It wasn't part of the requirements...so it's
not my concern...
This is getting interesting!

Later, when she showed the proposal documents to
Alpha, she received a harsh scolding.
Development postponed? Why?

*sigh* I've been doing a lot more work for the Garden
lately. I used to be more...free...to pursue my own
research.

Sure, it's a good thing the organization has grown
along with the scale of development...but...

They won't let me use money freely... Is Mitsugoshi...
not making money recently?

Is it time for me to look for my next home? If so,
I'll take Master along with me... Yeah.
Anyway, jokes aside... This is where it starts...
...Heh...hehehe!

Now that I've reached my quota, it's time for
my own research!

I managed to secure a budget...by saying they were
necessary expenses.

Research for the organization and research for
myself... What matters...is maintaining a balance
between the two...
Hehehe...hehe!

With a smile on her face, Eta enjoys herself into
the late hours of the night.
